{"name": "test_etcd_ha_failover_trtllm_aggregated", "status": "passed", "description": "\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries for TRT-LLM in aggregated mode.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and an aggregated TRT-LLM worker\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n    ", "attachments": [{"name": "log", "source": "2caa811d-c858-4987-b845-e2a9d22d663f-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stdout", "source": "c55f3c25-818a-454f-815e-434f7450872a-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stderr", "source": "92deb785-789f-4ee1-bcf8-1223785b8288-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}], "parameters": [{"name": "framework", "value": "'trtllm'"}, {"name": "platform", "value": "'amd64'"}, {"name": "test_type", "value": "'pre_merge_gpu'"}], "start": 1775684031498, "stop": 1775684117065, "uuid": "4cdb2b8e-c442-4a63-bb2c-bbb136e0e864", "historyId": "72142f7f91275244637eecaaa57a135a", "testCaseId": "e5f75e2c55f318720da5bb7098638912", "fullName": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_trtllm#test_etcd_ha_failover_trtllm_aggregated", "labels": [{"name": "dynamo_workflow", "value": "Nightly CI Pipeline"}, {"name": "dynamo_framework", "value": "trtllm"}, {"name": "dynamo_platform", "value": "amd64"}, {"name": "dynamo_testType", "value": "pre_merge_gpu"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "nightly"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "e2e"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "gpu_1"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "fault_tolerance"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "trtllm"}, {"name": "parentSuite", "value": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha"}, {"name": "suite", "value": "test_trtllm"}, {"name": "host", "value": "prod-tester-amd-gpu-v1-phg7c-